# This template uses npm (package-lock.json is the committed lockfile).
# Ignore other package managers' lockfiles so a stray `pnpm install` /
# `yarn install` here doesn't get committed — two lockfiles make Vercel/
# Netlify pick the wrong package manager.
pnpm-lock.yaml
yarn.lock
